room_title: Escape room "Carnival Conundrum" by Just Escape in New York
room_description: Come one, come all, step right up, and have a ball! Are you ready to head down to the most unique carnival of your life? Join us at Carnival Conundrum for bright lights, fun music, classic carnival games, freshly popped popcorn, and loads of fun! But beware, the wind is picking up and the dark clouds are rolling in. Can you make it through the carnival before the storm strikes?
